{"tid":2047093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WHO譚德塞：美國對全球健康有著巨大貢獻且慷慨大方","createTime":"2020-06-02T01:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T05:54:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":65,"dislike":307,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"6580bb9d6dea3baa28cf5ec9b4270969534623cf","tid":2047093,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:18:34.000Z","msg":"世界衛生組織秘書長譚德塞真的和美國總統川普一樣，都是「謎一樣的男人」。特別是譚德塞今年對抗新冠肺炎疫情期間，為了力挺中國大陸，不惜和美國總統川普大打口水戰，為此還失去了美國平均一年4.5億美元的贊助金援。<br />\n<br />\n但就在全球疫情趨穩的後疫情時代，譚德塞改口了，在剛結束的視訊會議上，大方讚美美國對全球健康有著巨大貢獻，還誇美國是一個慷慨大方的國家，譚德塞也改變不甩美國的態度，表態希望世界衛生組織未來能和美國繼續合作下去。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞態度的轉變，國際輿論的解讀是，中國大陸雖然願意在背後支持譚德塞，但總部位在瑞士的WHO，體系內還是偏歐美思維，尤其是在這次防疫作戰中，世衛的表現非常糟糕，讓譚德塞不得不正視並處理和美國之間的關係。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，美國的贊助金額一年4.52億美元，和中國大陸的4200萬美元相比真的差很大。而美國總統川普也表示，這筆原先要給世衛的經費，未來將轉投入其他公共衛生領域，不會白白浪費。至於美國要退出WHO的問題，譚德塞則沒有做出正面回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/005626272.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F005626272.html&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=045acd87\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/005626272.html</a>"},{"pid":"ed0343a2fd882f9bc41bdb075164ad86de832c3c","tid":2047093,"uid":2054,"like":91,"dislike":3,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:19:56.000Z","msg":"篤灰保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf808c4d0b8f05c8a2f7397a7a4206a94a45ab3","tid":2047093,"uid":8014,"like":284,"dislike":1,"score":283,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:22:52.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣死1萬次都唔夠<br />\n<br />\n害死全球30萬人"},{"pid":"af1243fd53cb2f3450c386aa5c0d7c06c599ca7c","tid":2047093,"uid":55386,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:23:10.000Z","msg":"賣口乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b22065a6848f925a7591920923155d2ae74959","tid":2047093,"uid":199957,"like":161,"dislike":1,"score":160,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:23:17.000Z","msg":"而美國總統川普也表示，這筆原先要給世衛的經費，未來將轉投入其他公共衛生領域，不會白白浪費。<br />\n<br />\nYA 咁奶共 你地自己慢慢玩"},{"pid":"59e46eb7df32c1778c6fb59ea806badc92750513","tid":2047093,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5011d66f6310490079778a8f51407b6047de3a14","tid":2047093,"uid":265839,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:23:48.000Z","msg":"It is too late"},{"pid":"2edcadae0261bab73e05948954859eacf1a0df34","tid":2047093,"uid":98291,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:24:09.000Z","msg":"尚書大人"},{"pid":"2c21599c048cd7a9f2b00f43c70b9f6f887fa270","tid":2047093,"uid":53604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:24:48.000Z","msg":"$$$$$$$$$$$$$"},{"pid":"e4e20adf19d99b8a03de8e9efbabd168ba816c93","tid":2047093,"uid":170249,"like":6,"dislike":29,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:25:28.000Z","msg":"似邊邊有利益就幫邊邊咁<br />\n<br />\ndllm侵侵玩大啲啦 屠殺力架 反正都連唔到任 順手開埋ww3 撚鳩下任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cd654d45e2a94a0b62d5f2993b29938fb13348","tid":2047093,"uid":31200,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:26:35.000Z","msg":"奶完共點知激嬲美帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住諗住講幾句好話，但人地睇穿晒你世衛有幾垃圾唔會再信你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843fc72a2b344128f62d3f0ff02bcb843ee303fd","tid":2047093,"uid":223385,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:27:03.000Z","msg":"等CIA上門啦, 柒碌..."},{"pid":"3158411e7690f9d2a451192be4c624dad446602e","tid":2047093,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu